      <title>随着信用质量开始恶化，垃圾债券的风险变得更大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-20/junk-bonds-get-riskier-as-credit-quality-starts-to-erode-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1.4 万亿美元的美国垃圾债券市场正变得越来越垃圾，因为越来越多的债务要么被降级，要么被提升，完全脱离高收益债券领域。奥利维亚·雷蒙德还有更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-20/junk-bonds-get-riskier-as-credit-quality-starts-to-erode-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 20:57:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
