    <item>
      <title>中国在抛售股票后冻结量化基金账户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-freezes-accounts-of-quant-fund-after-it-dumped-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，一家大型量化对冲基金在一分钟内抛售了 25.7 亿元人民币（约合 3.6 亿美元）的股票，中国两家主要证券交易所将该基金的账户冻结了三天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-freezes-accounts-of-quant-fund-after-it-dumped-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 12:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>货币政策不确定性盖过市场紧张，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对长期加息的担忧打压了更广泛的情绪，抵消了实物石油市场收紧的迹象，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 23:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在英伟达的成败时刻之前，股市下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技公司拖累股市脱离历史高点，华尔街等待英伟达公司周三公布的财报，以确认这家芯片制造商能否满足人工智能繁荣所设定的崇高期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
